# Code owners — the gate files. Any PR touching these requires the maintainer's
# (code-owner) approval, even from collaborators who have Write/merge access.
#
# Lab submissions live under submissions/ and are intentionally NOT owned here,
# so a community reviewer can merge a lab PR with just the lab-validate check
# green — no maintainer approval needed. But they CANNOT weaken the gates
# (CI workflow, validator, schema, deps) without the maintainer signing off.
#
# Replace @potik-admin with your maintainer GitHub username if different.

/.github/          @potik-admin
/scripts/          @potik-admin
/lab.schema.json   @potik-admin
/package.json      @potik-admin
/package-lock.json @potik-admin
